# Golden defaults

Preferred stack: Next.js + TypeScript + Tailwind for frontend. FastAPI for backend services. Supabase for auth, database, and storage. Use Docker for deployment. Deviate only if project requirements demand it.

See [docs/PHILOSOPHY.md](docs/PHILOSOPHY.md) for full rationale and template contents.
